      "range": "44-81",
      "markText": "以轻卒尝之，贱而勇者将之，期于北，毋期于得。为之微阵以触其侧。是谓大得。”",
      "totalCount": 66,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=721158&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=44&rangeEnd=81",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0732bf05b0106f07a916cd?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=44&rangeEnd=81"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "721158_19_0-59",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "0-59",
      "markText": "善者，敌人军人众，能使分离而不相救也，受敌而不相知也。故沟深垒高不得以为固，车坚兵利不得以为威，士有勇力而不得以为强。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "721158_1_350-422",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "350-422",
      "markText": "请遣轻车西驰梁郊，以怒其气。分卒而从之，示之寡。”于是为之。庞子果弃其辎重，兼趣舍而至。孙子弗息而击之桂陵，而擒庞涓。故曰，孙子之所以为者尽矣。",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=721158&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=350&rangeEnd=422",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0732bf05b0106f07a916cd?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=350&rangeEnd=422"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "721158_1_187-211",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "187-211",
      "markText": "孙子曰：“都大夫孰为不识事？”曰：“齐城、高唐。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=721158&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=187&rangeEnd=211",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0732bf05b0106f07a916cd?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=187&rangeEnd=211"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "721158_18_467-521",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "467-521",
      "markText": "是以按左右，右败而左弗能救；按右左，左败而右弗能救。是以兵坐而不起，避而不用，近者少而不足用，远者疏而不能。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=721158&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=521",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0732bf05b0106f07a916cd?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=521"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "721158_9_0-100",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "0-100",
      "markText": "孙子曰：夫陷齿戴角，前爪后距，喜而合，怒而斗，天之道也，不可止也。故无天兵者自为备，圣人之事也。黄帝作剑，以阵象之。羿作弓弩，以势象之。禹作舟车，以变象之。汤、武作长兵，以权象之。凡此四者，兵之用也。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "721158_19_176-266",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "176-266",
      "markText": "善者四路必彻，五动必工。故进不可迎于前，退不可绝于后，左右不可陷于阻，默［然而处］，于敌之人。故使敌四路必穷，五动必忧。进则傅于前，退则绝于后，左右则陷于阻，默然而处，军不免于患。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=721158&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=176&rangeEnd=266",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0732bf05b0106f07a916cd?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=176&rangeEnd=266"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "721158_21_0-25",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "0-25",
      "markText": "欲以敌国之民之所不安，正俗所难敌国兵之所长，耗兵也",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "721158_16_656-729",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "656-729",
      "markText": "交和而舍，敌人保山而带阻，我远则不接，近则无所，击之奈何？击此者，彼阻移则危之，攻其所必救，使离其固，以揆其虑，施伏设援，击其移庶。此击保固之道也",
      "totalCount": 33,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=721158&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=656&rangeEnd=729",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0732bf05b0106f07a916cd?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=656&rangeEnd=729"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "721158_2_66-92",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "66-92",
      "markText": "然夫乐兵者亡，而利胜者辱。兵非所乐也，而胜非所利也。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=721158&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=66&rangeEnd=92",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0732bf05b0106f07a916cd?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=66&rangeEnd=92"
    },
    {
